trans-unit.source:
It is no longer possible to do DateTimeWidget().options[&lsquo;a&rsquo;] = &lsquo;foo&rsquo;
or DateTimeWidget().date_options[&lsquo;a&rsquo;] = &lsquo;foo&rsquo;.  If you need to change
options imperatively, set the entire .options/.date_options dictionary.

required labels no longer insert an asterisk inside a &lt;span class=&rdquo;req&rdquo;&gt;
inside themselves.  instead the label element has a required class
if the field is required; use form.css to display this as an asterisk.
